Mobile device manufacturer, Xiaomi, has renewed competition in Nigeria with the unveiling of the 12 Series brand for the local market.
  
Xiaomi 12 Series, which was designed to empower users around the world with a cutting-edge videography studio and entertainment powerhouse, delivers impressive advancements in Xiaomi’s AI algorithm, flagship processing power, and an all-round elevated experience.
   
The Xiaomi 12 Pro enables users to record studio-quality shots no matter the scenario, be it challenging lighting conditions or moving objects. It boasts a pro-grade triple camera array for versatile shooting, starring a massive 50MP main wide angle camera, with 8K recording capabilities. 